text: Walter Kaiser (born 29 April 1971) is an Austrian rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Austria Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Klagenfurt
